# Kando dev server

When the user wants Kando running locally, use the **kando-dev-server** skill and run:

```bash
./scripts/kando-dev.sh start   # or stop | restart | status
```

Always serve from **this repository**, not an old Venubase worktree copy. Verify with `status` that `cwd` is the Kando repo before saying it is running.

Report the URL: **http://127.0.0.1:3001**
